{"tid":358293,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"煙鏟們可否帶走你啲煙頭？","createTime":"2017-08-13T15:36:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-18T11:08:24.000Z","uid":65473,"like":108,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"92fe9e030f332de13b050521c568c9bc260d42d3","tid":358293,"uid":65473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T15:36:29.000Z","msg":"成地都係煙頭煙盒<br />\n清潔香港真係靠撚晒你哋呀<br />\n明明有垃圾桶喺隔離都唔掉去個兜到<br />\n平時做火車頭呢啲惡行都唔同你計喇<br />\n當你哋真係搵唔到地方食先喺條街食<br />\n但食完可唔可以將啲垃圾放返喺應該放嘅地方？<br />\n行兩步就一支行多幾步又一支<br />\n如果你真係搵唔到地方掉煙頭<br />\n我建議返你帶埋個煙灰缸出街<br />\n成地都係垃圾搞到人好炆呀<br />\n好似返到去大陸地方咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb684fc9e199eae86d971957fbc247f202544ffb","tid":358293,"uid":65473,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T15:55:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/13/235431_3de6ac23bda99e04a5691c3da487ed53.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F13%2F235431_3de6ac23bda99e04a5691c3da487ed53.jpg&h=bebfeee3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n邊方面有困難？"},{"pid":"77007c808521fddcfdee996a60f33620442fa47e","tid":358293,"uid":6347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T15:57:30.000Z","msg":"D友成日掉垃圾落煙果格搞到又著火又無位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2a8e09291eb05e9792a00eef758840f0b5c265c","tid":358293,"uid":65473,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T15:59:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>D友成日掉垃圾落煙果格搞到又著火又無位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以咪叫你帶個煙灰缸出街囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79972b9ce7a53c72b89df714fd39c88206d393dc","tid":358293,"uid":65473,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T16:09:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/14/000845_88fd0fa081b7e0827a7738d509e597fa.jpg\