亂掉煙頭呢個行為<br />\n屌你老母煙頭唔撚係垃圾啊<br />\n周圍食煙亂掉正仆街<br />\n食得有啲公德得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ni57extq\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fni57extq&h=d1362293&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f9711cdbfb65f4b116b8fa1b6c1e74ee8b23bb69","tid":358293,"uid":77569,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T03:37:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9a7623026ebfd73d226f883369b1fef940941d6b","tid":358293,"uid":69098,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T03:43:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我想問，唔丟落地可以丟邊？<br />\n又唔係周圍有垃圾筒<br />\n唔通限住有垃圾筒先俾食？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實有啲專for戶外食完煙收煙灰煙頭嘅產品<br />\n無印已經有 而家教撚埋你 唔撚該快啲去買<br />\n唔好咁撚大聲合理化亂掉煙頭呢個行為<br />\n屌你老母煙頭唔撚係垃圾啊<br />\n周圍食煙亂掉正仆街<br />\n食得有啲公德得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ni57extq\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fni57extq&h=d1362293&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n你下次喺街食餅記住拎埋個碟盛住d碎<br />\n食魚蛋唔好烏前食喎，滴落自己件衫好喇</blockquote><br />\n依家唔係同你計啲煙灰呀垃圾<br />\n食完啲餅包裝袋同魚蛋竹籤冇垃圾桶我會放入袋或者拎住<br />\n同你計煙頭，你就攞煙灰嚟講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係食煙食到傻咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a67117ff62634ec6efcbc43a7880fed6ecdfca5e","tid":358293,"uid":9391,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T03:45:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我想問，唔丟落地可以丟邊？<br />\n又唔係周圍有垃圾筒<br />\n唔通限住有垃圾筒先俾食？</blockquote><br />\n你塞入你老母個西到啦 屌你老母"},{"pid":"3f716acae4fdc9e21370e34a25baddd450bd4832","tid":358293,"uid":56115,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T03:45:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我想問，唔丟落地可以丟邊？<br />\n又唔係周圍有垃圾筒<br />\n唔通限住有垃圾筒先俾食？</blockquote><br />\n你肚痛條街無廁所，你會唔會隨地？"},{"pid":"dba8bb817c226eba371e035d8ee4968a845ddab6","tid":358293,"uid"